<br>
&quot;You come here, you sit down have drink. Me tell you tale of me life.&quot;<br>
&quot;what? you not want hear? you be say me not interestin'?&quot;<br>
<br>
Veloxia growls deep in her throat.<br>
You sit back down and bury your face in your mug of ale...it's going to be a long night.<br>
Veloxia takes a long draught of Honey mead and begins her tale...<br>
<br>
&quot;Me was brought up by everyone. Me never had home, me was just wander 'round an' people take me in an' take care o' me 'til they be get sick o' me. Me been raised by Stinky Trolls, Overweight Ogres, Half elf bastards, Dirty old dwarves, itty bitty(even to me) Gnomes, and even a wood elf princess-in-exile.&quot;<br>
<br>
Veloxia glares as she watches you eye her incredulously.<br>
<br>
&quot;It be true! me swears all over meself!&quot; <br>
&quot;Me was abandoned baby, child of War. Me parents both died minutes after me was born, they town be taken over by Trolls. There be was a lady troll bigger than the rest... she takes me in an' be feels sorry fer me. She beat the other meanie trolls away with big stick, they want eat me but she not let 'em be do that. Methinks she had saw her daughter die in the war too an wanted family ta replace her. She raise me feed me an' send me on me way when me old enough ta survive shethinks. she taught me speak an' she taught me ta survive an' fight fer food an' how ta barsh froggies best. That be why me speaks diff'r'nt than everyone else 'round here. me was 6 when shes kick me out.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;Then me was raised by nearby Ogre village. Stop interrup'n me! Yes me raised by WHOLE village. nobody would take me in, but they toss me foods an' make sure me still livin' everyday. Me not stay there long, Ogre an' troll country smell yuk. So then me was about 8 years. Me snuck on boat and end up in this place they be call Butcherblock. Me gets chased by goblins into city of dwarfs. This dwarf take me in(me not know whether man or woman, they all look same an' ugly, me no care). This dwarf take care me, but it dirty and drink lots an' talk nasty an' want me do yukky things. Me not like there so me go away again.&quot;<br>
<br>
Veloxia finishes her third Mead and burps loudly.<br>
<br>
&quot;Like me saying... me went ta greatdark forest. Me found pretty Half elf bastard lady. me tag along with her an she feed me an tell me shut up all times. she put on lots face paint an' not wear much. she go ta work like when me be go bed. she come back late an' sometimes she scream alot 'til morning. Me was always tired. me can't sleep with she be scream at night all night. so me go. me 10 years now.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;me find gnomes living in windmill. methinks this weird, but they be nice. they not like way me talk an' way me paint face like half-elf lady. they make me do it less. they say me look like whore 'n say they make me decent. they was nice, but they frustrate easy. they give up after 3 week an' me not change. they say they go back ta science an' no more fiddle with careless haffings.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;last place me 'member be the wood elf princess... she was beautiful. she was very nice, only nice person that stay nice an' not try change or yell me at. she tell me she kicked out by other elves an' they be say she be sacrilige an' they not like her god. Her god was Rallos Zek. She tell me lots 'bout him. she tell me me was child of war an' me should become mighty Warrior, an' follow Rallos Zek. she gave me magic potion, an' when me drink it made me have weird dream. me talk ta Rallos an' he tell me how ta be mighty warrior. He be tell me kill all that stand in way. He tell me feed him blood. He tell me wreak vengeance on everything that be done thing not nice ta me. Melikes Rallos, and me say me follow him always. Me then wakey from dream. Everything be black an' on fire.... it smell bad. Me found Elf lady body an' me cry over it. then me pray ta Rallos an' tell him me forever wreak vengeance on those that would do thing like this. me be his child of war. me was 15 then. me followed bandits an' kill em all that day.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;ever since, me be go 'round kill all things me not like. all things me see do mean things. all things that get in me way me kill too. if it stink or if it ugly me kills too.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;then me meets Andlie. Me knows me loves her first time me sees her. She beautiful haffing cleric with silky hair, Luscious lips, an' big smile. She nicest person me be ever met. Ever since that day me always with her. If she not be with me you not be find her anywheres. She say shes love me too, an' we be together 'til even now! We gets married soon. Rallos an' her god Bristlebane say we get married in Solusek eye. they be say we get Melded together to be one like in lava. Me loves her much... more than me ever thoughts me could love anything. Me loves her even mnore than me loves killing!&quot;<br>
<br>
Andlie enters the tavern from the doorway to the cleric guild founded for Brell.<br>
Andlie looks around, and walks over toward Veloxia's table, waking up her audience before Veloxia notices.<br>
<br>
Veloxia looks up, and pounces on andlie, and wraps her arms around her.<br>
<br>
&quot;we go now, Love, me drunk an' you gots you new spells oi?&quot;<br>
<br>
Veloxia waves to the deaf patron and stumbles out the door... arm in arm with the most beautiful halfling woman on Norrath or Luclin. <br>
<br>
Veloxia the Lucky One. Andlie's One. <p><BR><B>Veloxia Voluptuous </B><BR>
